!discord-bridge/data/.gitkeep
# Stray repo-root data dir: the canonical data dir is discord-bridge/data, but a
# CWD-relative write in bot/main.py drops last_startup_meeting.txt into ./data when
# the bot/tests run from the repo root. Leading slash anchors this to the root so it
# never matches discord-bridge/data.
/data/

# Scratch Scripts
test_funding.py
